document_data.caption: A map showing Julbuck Alley in the Dock Ward of Waterdeep.
document_data.name: Julbuck Alley
document_data.mainbody: '''Julbuck Alley''' was a small backalley that was located in the city of [[Waterdeep]].{{Cite interactive atlas|Waterdeep}}
document_data.Location: Julbuck Alley was located in Waterdeep's [[Waterdeep/Dock Ward|Dock Ward]]. The alley branched off of [[Picklock Alley]], passing due south before turning east to terminate at a dead end after several buildings.
